prospects for the pawn.}) 9... Qxa4 10. Nxa4 Ne4 {The pawn on d4 strongly
restricts White's mobility.} 11. Bg3 (11. Rxd4 Nxf2 $19) 11... Nc6 (11... Bg5+
$1 12. Kb1 Bf5 13. Ka1 Nc6 14. Nf3 Bf6 $17) 12. Nf3 Nxc5 13. Nxc5 Bxc5 $15 14.
Ne5 Nxe5 15. Bxe5 Bf5 16. g4 {Ilincic,Z (2565)-Vukovic,Z (2470) Yugoslavia
