hxg6 22. Nb5 Ne6 23. Qb7 (23. Qd6 $2 a6 {wins the knight.}) 23... dxe4 24. fxe4
Nc5 25. Qxa7 Nxe4 $17) 7... Bxd3 8. Qxd3 c6 9. Nge2 ({Or if} 9. Nf3 Nbd7 10. h3
O-O 11. O-O Re8 12. Qc2 Nb6 {As we know, a knight on this square is an
