{6.dxc5 is an ambitious, but risky move. How Black should develop the
initiative?} 6... d4 $1 {Black refrains from retrieving the pawn and prefers
to gain space in the centre. This implies a pawn sacrifice, but quite a
promising one, as White will have problems with his development.} 7. Nb5 e5 $1
{It is essential to keep the molesting pawn on d4.} 8. Nxe5 a6 $1 9. Na3 O-O $1
